<article/eans> ns4kge:mentionsNSMethod <ns-method/structure-aware-negative-sampling> .
<article/eans> ns4kge:mentionsNSMethod <ns-method/uniform-negative-sampling> .
<article/eans> ns4kge:mentionsKGEModel <kge-model/transe> .
<article/eans> ns4kge:mentionsKGEModel <kge-model/distmult> .
<article/eans> ns4kge:mentionsKGEModel <kge-model/complex> .
<article/eans> ns4kge:mentionsKGEModel <kge-model/transd> .
